      <description>ã€&#xA;          &lt;table width=&#34;100%&#34; border=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td width=80 valign=top&gt;&#xA;                &lt;img src=&#34;https://elixirstatus.com/rss/avatar/ketupia?uid=J3ISj&#34; width=&#34;64&#34; height=&#34;64&#34; /&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td&gt;&#xA;                &lt;h1&gt;Introducing AshStudio: A VS Code Extension for the Ash Framework&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                     8 Aug 2025&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    by&#xA;                    &lt;i class=&#34;icon-git_circle&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt; ketupia&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color=&#34;#aaa&#34;&gt;&#xA;                    &#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;p&gt;&#xA;AshStudio is a Visual Studio Code extension purpose-built for Ash Framework projects. With AshStudio, you get a better experience for building Elixir applications with Ash.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;ğŸš€ Key Features&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Intuitive Section Navigation&lt;/strong&gt;:  Jump between top-level sections of your Ash resources with Ctrl+Shift+P, breadcrumbs, and a custom sidebar. The extension parses your codebase, so navigation is always context-aware and lightning fast.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Jump-to-Definition&lt;/strong&gt;: Ctrl+Click navigation to actions, aggegates, attributes, calculations, and resource definitions.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt; Mermaid Diagram Generation and Viewing with CodeLens&lt;/strong&gt;: Instantly visualize relationships and resource diagrams right in your editor. CodeLens annotations provide one-click access to diagrams, making it easier to understand and communicate your architecture.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;Available in both the Microsoft store and OpenVSX.  Check out the &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/ketupia/ash-studio-vscode-extension&#34;&gt;github repo&lt;/a&gt; for more.  &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;hr&gt;&#xA;                &lt;small&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://elixirstatus.com/p/J3ISj-introducing-ashstudio-a-vs-code-extension-for-the-ash-framework&#34;&gt;View on ElixirStatus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;        ã€‘&lt;table width =â€œ 100ï¼…â€ border =â€œ 0â€&gt;&#xA;            &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;tdå®½åº¦= 80 valign = top&gt;&#xA;                &lt;img src =â€œ https://elixirstatus.com/rss/avatar/ketupia?uid=j3isjâ€ width =â€œ 64â€ height =â€œ 64â€/&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td&gt;&#xA;                &lt;h1&gt;ä»‹ç»Ashstudioï¼šASHæ¡†æ¶çš„VSä»£ç æ‰©å±•å&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;font color =â€œï¼ƒaaaâ€&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color =â€œï¼ƒaaaâ€&gt;&#xA;                     2025å¹´8æœˆ8æ—¥&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color =â€œï¼ƒaaaâ€&gt;&#xA;                    ç»è¿‡&#xA;                    &lt;i class =â€œ icon-git_circleâ€&gt; &lt;/i&gt; ketupia&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color =â€œï¼ƒaaaâ€&gt;&#xA;                    &#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;p&gt;&#xA;Ashstudioæ˜¯ç”¨äºASHæ¡†æ¶é¡¹ç›®çš„è§†è§‰å·¥ä½œå®¤ä»£ç æ‰©å±•ã€‚ä½¿ç”¨Ashstudioï¼Œæ‚¨å¯ä»¥è·å¾—æ›´å¥½çš„ä½“éªŒï¼Œå¯ä»¥ä½¿ç”¨Ashæ„å»ºé•¿ç”Ÿä¸è€è¯ã€‚&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;ğŸš€å…³é”®åŠŸèƒ½&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;ç›´è§‚éƒ¨åˆ†å¯¼èˆª&lt;/strong&gt;ï¼šä½¿ç”¨Ctrl+Shift+Pï¼Œé¢åŒ…å±‘å’Œè‡ªå®šä¹‰ä¾§è¾¹æ ä¹‹é—´çš„ç°åˆ†èµ„æºçš„é¡¶çº§éƒ¨åˆ†è·³è·ƒã€‚æ‰©å±•ç¨‹åºè§£ææ‚¨çš„ä»£ç åº“ï¼Œå› æ­¤å¯¼èˆªå§‹ç»ˆæ˜¯ä¸Šä¸‹æ–‡æ„ŸçŸ¥çš„ï¼Œå¹¶ä¸”å¿«é€Ÿé—ªç”µã€‚&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;è·³åˆ°å®šä¹‰&lt;/strong&gt;ï¼šCTRL+å•å‡»å¯¼èˆªåˆ°åŠ¨ä½œï¼Œaggegatesï¼Œå±æ€§ï¼Œè®¡ç®—å’Œèµ„æºå®šä¹‰ã€‚&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;ä½¿ç”¨Codelensçš„ç¾äººé±¼å›¾ç”Ÿæˆå’Œè§‚çœ‹&lt;/strong&gt;ï¼šç«‹å³å¯è§†åŒ–ç¼–è¾‘å™¨ä¸­çš„å…³ç³»å’Œèµ„æºå›¾ã€‚ Codelensæ³¨é‡Šæä¾›äº†ä¸€é”®å¼è®¿é—®å›¾è¡¨çš„è®¿é—®ï¼Œä½¿æ‚¨æ›´å®¹æ˜“ç†è§£å’Œä¼ è¾¾æ‚¨çš„ä½“ç³»ç»“æ„ã€‚&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;åœ¨Microsoft Storeå’ŒOpenVSXä¸Šéƒ½å¯ä»¥ä½¿ç”¨ã€‚  è¯·æŸ¥çœ‹&lt;a href =â€œ https://github.com/ketupia/ash-studio-vscode-extensionâ€&gt; github repo &lt;/a&gt;ä»¥è·å–æ›´å¤šä¿¡æ¯ã€‚  &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;hr&gt;&#xA;                &lt;small&gt; &lt;A href =â€œ https://elixirstatus.com/p/j3isj-introducing-ashstudio-a-vs-code-code-extension-extension-foror-the-hash-frameworkâ€&gt;åœ¨Elixirstatusä¸ŠæŸ¥çœ‹&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/small&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/table&gt;</description>
